//to show all databases
show dbs

to go inside DB
use databasename as use novintern

see all the collection or tables
show collections

to find all data 
db.collectionname.find()
db.collectionname.find().pretty()

to create new databasename
use databasename 

/* database will only create when it has a collection, and collection will only be created when it has a data. */

to insert a record 
db.user.insert({_id:1, name:'json'})
--> verify by:
use novintern 
show dbs




